Class ChainedCompressor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.cassandra.io.compress.ChainedCompressor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.cassandra.io.compress.ICompressor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EncryptingDeflateCompressor, EncryptingLZ4Compressor, EncryptingSnappyCompressor

    public abstract class ChainedCompressor
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.cassandra.io.compress.ICompressor
    Allows for chaining multiple compressors, so output of one compressor is input of another.
